eric singer th anniversary snare drum  pearl drums cart tweet limited edition eric singer th anniversary snare drum own a hand crafted one of a kind instrument from pearl limited edition items are produced with the high level of craftsmanship but are enhanced with the exclusive finishes and shell compositions dont miss your chance to add these instantly collectible instruments to your arsenal features in tribute to  years of drumming together on stages all over the world pearl and kiss drummer eric singer recently collaborated to create a new limited edition signature drum with a nod to one of the great snares of pearl’s past “i collect classic and vintage pearl drums” says eric “i love the sound and feel of the original jupiter chromeoverbrass models from the ’s and really wanted to explore that sound with an updated feel” the result is eric’s new th anniversary limited edition signature snare released on the heels of singer and pearl’s successful charity drum auction for the lifeline charter school in  eric’s new snare begins with a dualbeaded jupiterstyle mm chromeplated brass shell in contrast to the jupiter’s original parallel action strainer eric’s limited signature update features pearl’s compact clicklock throwoff for smooth sensitive response each drum assures tuning accuracy with pearl’s lowcontact cl bridge lugs and features a personally signed attack es signature drumhead similar to last year’s auction drum all artist royalties from the sale of eric’s th anniversary limited snare will benefit school music and arts programs at the lifeline education charter school in compton ca “it has been an honor and pleasure to play pearl drums for over  years and counting” singer says “they have truly given me the best reason to play drums” model essc shells x dualbeaded jupiterstyle mm chromeplated brass shell finish chrome hoops shb  shs lugs cl rods sst tension rod x  snares snn eric singer project  wikipedia eric singer project from wikipedia the free encyclopedi