 symphony and angel of babylon in  he served as gary moores drummer on the wild frontier tour in  he made a brief appearance in the wes craven film shocker as a member of a fictional rock band in  singer was featured on italian rock singer chris catenas debut album freak out he recorded drums for two tracks sweet talker a whitesnake cover and the stronger you are the harder you fall in  singer was elected to the jury of watchmakings highest awards the grand prix dhorlogerie de genève gphg he is a well known in collectors circles as a collector of eclectic timepieces from his home town favorite ball to expensive glashutte origina zenith omega and iwc his keen eye to mechanics and artistic design encouraged the gphg to invite him to join the rotating group of  jurors in geneva this november as they select the best watches of  eric singer performing with alice cooper equipmentedit throughout his career singer has used pearl drums hardware and pedals terry bozzio attack signature drumheads zildjian cymbals and ddrum acoustic drum triggers singer has his own signature series snare drum and artist series drumsticks by pearl and zildjian also makes its own eric singer artist series drumsticks discographyedit solo  eric singer projectedit main article eric singer project lost and spaced  esp  esp live in japan  esp live at the marquee referencesedit leaf david ken sharp  kiss behind the mask – the official authorized biography new york ny warner books inc isbn   sherman dale  black diamond the unauthorized biography of kiss th anniversary edition burlington on canada cg publishing ltd isbn   notesedit  top  jewish rock stars  ultimate classic rock ultimateclassicrockcomtopjewishockstars dec    trex lead singer and guitarist marc bolan was born mark feld  jewish rockers in kiss including simmons bruce kulick and eric singer  these jews rock  aishcom wwwaishcomjasthesejewsrockhtml jun    half its members are jewish if you count later members bruce kulick and eric singer then 