events july    pmbridge tender innjuly    pmcortez kitchenjuly    pmisland time bar  grillaugust    pmjake’s american bar loews royal pacific resort aec v home page be mine for a little while music video check our erics brand new it’s finally here check out the eric von’s new ep “be mine for a little while” check out the eric von’s new video bio click here to listen to eric von’s single “i can’t help but smile” that climbed to  on the music row charts   i was born and raised in cortez which is a small fishing village in the bradenton beach area of the gulf coast in southwest florida i am one of three boys i have an older brother and a twin brother being raised a stones throw from the water i obviously enjoy almost anything that involves the water my favorites are surfing diving and fishing but my real true passion is music i write my own lyrics and music infusing my country tunes with an island flair i have been singing since i was three years old it was at the age of twelve that i started playing the guitar and by the time i was fourteen i was performing professionally i have had the opportunity to meet and work with a lot of great people but some of my best moments were when i opened for kenny chesney miranda lambert jake owen aaron tippin and john anderson i also had the chance to meet david lee murphy and to sit down and write with nashville’s own kim tribble i now reside in orlando and play regularly at jimmy buffett’s margaritaville at universal city walk… read more home page contact privacy policy copyright  pearl x limited edition eric singer snare  just drums  willowdale ave toronto on favourites cart login  register  email  first name  last name × product categoriesselect a category drums    in stock showroom specials    acoustic    electronic       yamaha dtx instant savings    snare drums    used gear cymbals    china    crash    ride    splash    box set    effects    hihats    zildjian k custom special dry    paiste colour sound     sabian effects  har