ensitive response each drum is signed by eric and assures tuning accuracy with pearl’s low‐contact cl bridge lugs similar to last year’s auction drum all artist royalties from the sale of eric’s th anniversary limited snare will benefit school music and arts programs at the lifeline education charter school in compton ca “it has been an honor and pleasure to play pearl drums for over  years and counting” singer says “they have truly given me the best reason to play drums” pearl ″x″ limited edition eric singer snare sku esascadd to favouritesproduct added browse wishlistthe product is already in the wishlist browse wishlist  add to cart you may also like… pearl demonator p double bass pedal brand pearl  add to cart you might also like pearl midtown  piece shell pack black cherry glitter  add to cart gretsch catalina club   piece gloss antique burst  add to cart sold used pearl vision birch bop kit  piece champagne sparkle  read more gretsch renown maple  piece satin tobacco burst  add to cart yamaha live oak custom  piece amber shadow sunburst  add to cart eric singer – kiss pick world skip to navigation skip to content   items your source for official kiss guitar picks eric singer sort by popularity sort by newness sort by price low to high sort by price high to low showing – of  results kiss kruise vi eric singer sailaway pick  add to cart kiss kruise vi eric singer night  pick  add to cart kiss kruise vi eric singer night  pick  add to cart kiss kruise vi eric singer glow in the dark creatures pick  add to cart kiss kruise vi eric singer creatures of the deep blue sea pick  add to cart kiss kruise vi eric singer ikon pick  add to cart  europe common guitar pick eric singer  add to cart  europe flames guitar pick eric singer  add to cart  south america common guitar pick eric singer  add to cart  south america flames guitar pick eric singer  add to cart kiss kruise v alive guitar pick eric singer  add to cart  new zealand flag guitar pick eric singer  add to cart s